OL,3,CFamily urge travellers to pack carbon
OL,4,Cmonoxide alarm year on from son's death
OL,6,F"The travel industry has done a lot.
OL,7,FIt doesn't mean the world is safe.
OL,9,F"That's why the campaign is about
OL,10,Fmaking sure travellers are equipped
OL,11,Fwith the knowledge of the symptoms of
OL,12,Fcarbon monoxide poisoning and people
OL,13,Fshould take an alarm with them."
OL,15,FA carbon monoxide alarm can cost
OL,16,Faround #20, something Hudson's family
OL,17,Fsay is a small price to pay to save a
OL,18,Flife.
